    "name": "CMS - Basic Health & Info API",
    "description": "Basic Health and Information API collection for the Clinic Management System with Clean Architecture.\n\n## üè• Server Health & Info API\n\nThis collection focuses specifically on basic server health and information endpoints:\n\n- **Health Check**: Monitor server health and status\n- **API Information**: Get API version and basic information\n- **Server Status**: Check server connectivity and response times\n- **Environment Info**: Retrieve environment-specific information\n- **Uptime Monitoring**: Track server uptime and availability\n- **Basic Connectivity**: Test basic API connectivity\n\n## Testing Coverage\n\n- ‚úÖ Health check endpoint testing\n- ‚úÖ API information retrieval\n- ‚úÖ Server status verification\n- ‚úÖ Response time monitoring\n- ‚úÖ Basic connectivity testing\n- ‚úÖ Environment information access\n- ‚úÖ Error handling for server issues\n- ‚úÖ Uptime and availability monitoring\n\n## Environment Variables\n\nThis collection uses the following environment variables:\n- `cms_local`: http://localhost:4000 (for local development)\n- `cms_prod`: https://capstone-api.up.railway.app (for production)\n- `baseUrl`: Base URL for API endpoints\n- Various test data variables for dynamic testing",
